WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:14.362
Branching — Commit & Rollback

00:00:14.362 --> 00:00:33.413
Commits, branches, checkout

00:00:33.413 --> 00:00:48.026
Step 1: Version one

00:00:48.026 --> 00:01:06.804
Step 2: Real data, three rows

00:01:06.804 --> 00:01:29.355
Step 3: Commit it

00:01:29.355 --> 00:01:39.601
Step 4: Name it with a branch

00:01:39.601 --> 00:01:54.864
Step 5: Keep working, version two

00:01:54.864 --> 00:02:11.431
Step 6: Disaster strikes the table

00:02:11.431 --> 00:02:30.666
Step 7: The table is gone

00:02:30.666 --> 00:02:46.866
Step 8: Commit the broken state

00:02:46.866 --> 00:03:05.323
Step 9: The history

00:03:05.323 --> 00:03:23.801
Step 10: Check the branch out

00:03:23.801 --> 00:03:40.526
Step 11: Start the rollback

00:03:40.526 --> 00:03:56.975
Step 12: Proof: version one

00:03:56.975 --> 00:04:14.770
Step 13: The data is back

00:04:14.470 --> 00:04:29.236
Both versions, side by side

00:04:28.936 --> 00:04:38.856
Next: Live Migration
